snippet.textDisplay:
I had heard this song numerous times. Loved the composition, picturization, yet another Coke Studio Pakistan masterpiece. And life moved on. 
Then 2 years later, one fine morning,  YouTube autoplayed it. It happened to me when I was going through a mental turmoil, and coping with a few griefs. 
It spoke to me like an angel, a Saint, a philosopher friend. I cried, replayed, cried more, on loop!
It is the strongest I have felt for a song, ever in my life. 
Thank you to the makers.
Love from India. ❤
